- Arduino Mega
- 3x4 matrix membrane keypad (requires 7 wires to connect to Arduino)
- I2C enabled LCD (requires 4 wires to connect to Arduino)

======== 3x4 membrane connection ========

R1-R2-R3-R4-C1-C2-C3
R1: Pin 38
R2: Pin 39
R3: Pin 40
R4: Pin 41
C1: Pin 42
C2: Pin 43
C3: Pin 44

======== I2C enabled LCD ========

LCD Pin Ground: Ground Pin of Arduino
LCD Pin VCC: 5V Pin of Arduino
LCD Pin SDA: Pin 20
LCD Pin SCL: Pin 21